## 5. Professional Polish & Accessibility

- **Transitions:** `transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out`
- **Focus states:**  
  `focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2`
- **Contrast:** White text on gradients only
- **Shadows:** `shadow-corporate`, `shadow-corporate-md`
- **Mobile First:** `flex-col`, `grid-cols-1`

### Common Mistakes to Avoid
❌ Black text on gradients  
❌ Mixing Gold + Blue without context  
❌ Hardcoded paddings  
❌ Custom button styles  
❌ Using dark icon gradient (`#2E5AAC → #1C3667`) - use lighter gradient instead
❌ Inconsistent icon sizes across dashboard cards

